Recently I visited @tilara_polyplast at #acetech 

I was impressed with the amazing products ..
They also have launched new product ie glass like polycarbonate sheet which is just amazing ! 

It’s like half the weight of glass, easy installation, and handling, sustainability, 250 times stronger than glass. 

This product solves problems of millions of developers and fabricators and is mostly used for Interior & exterior railing, shower cubicles and facades.

I couldn’t find a single reason not to prefer Tilara over glass.

They also have other products like ,
Polycarbonate Solid Sheet & Roll
Polycarbonate Multiwall Sheet
Polycarbonate Profiled Sheet
TPPLGLAS XT Acrylic Sheet
GPPS Sheet
GPPS Textured Sheet
Light Diffuser Sheet
Lighting Profiles

So start replacing glass with Tilara Polycarbonate sheets now !!

Hello everyone! 👋

Firstly welcome to all new members who have joined me recently!! 

Let me give you a short introduction!

So Welcome to my Instagram page, where I share my passion for interior design and Architecture.

My name is Pragya ,and I’m an interior designer.
We do projects in all over Maharashtra.

 I love creating beautiful and functional spaces that make people happy and comfortable. On this page, you will find examples of my work. You will also get to know me better as a person and as a designer. 

Thank you for joining me on this journey, and feel free to ask me about any work enquiry, you can just dm me or WhatsApp me directly 
I would love to hear from you!
